sequenceDiagram
    title 图片解析流程 (P0-2)
    actor User
    participant KBView as KnowledgeBaseView
    participant KBStore as knowledge_base store
    participant KBAPI as knowledge_base API
    participant DocSvc as DocumentService
    participant ImgParser as ImageParser
    participant LLMSvc as LLMService
    participant EmbedSvc as EmbeddingService
    participant Chroma as ChromaService
    participant MySQL

    User->>KBView: 上传图片文件 (.jpg/.png)
    KBView->>KBStore: uploadDocument(kbId, file)
    KBStore->>KBAPI: POST /{kb_id}/documents (multipart)
    KBAPI->>DocSvc: upload_document(user_id, kb_id, content, filename)
    DocSvc->>MySQL: INSERT KBDocument (status=pending)
    DocSvc-->>KBAPI: doc (id=123)
    KBAPI-->>KBStore: doc response
    KBStore-->>KBView: 文档已上传
    KBView->>KBView: 启动 3s 轮询

    Note over DocSvc: 后台异步处理
    DocSvc->>MySQL: UPDATE status=processing
    DocSvc->>ImgParser: parse(file_path, llm_service, llm_config)
    ImgParser->>ImgParser: 读取文件 → base64 编码
    ImgParser->>LLMSvc: analyze_image(base64, prompt)
    LLMSvc-->>ImgParser: {summary, detailed_analysis}
    ImgParser-->>DocSvc: 文本描述字符串
    DocSvc->>DocSvc: split_text(description) → chunks
    DocSvc->>EmbedSvc: embed_texts(chunk_texts)
    EmbedSvc-->>DocSvc: embeddings[][]
    DocSvc->>MySQL: INSERT KBChunk × N
    DocSvc->>Chroma: add_chunks(kb_id, ids, texts, embeddings, metadatas)
    DocSvc->>MySQL: UPDATE status=completed, chunk_count=N
    Note over KBView: 3s 轮询检测到 status=completed → 停止轮询

---
    title 重索引流程 (P1-4)
    actor User2 as User
    participant KBView2 as KnowledgeBaseView
    participant KBAPI2 as knowledge_base API
    participant DocSvc2 as DocumentService
    participant EmbedSvc2 as EmbeddingService
    participant Chroma2 as ChromaService
    participant Redis2 as Redis
    participant MySQL2 as MySQL

    User2->>KBView2: 切换嵌入模型 → 点击「重索引」
    KBView2->>KBAPI2: POST /{kb_id}/reindex
    KBAPI2->>Redis2: SET reindex:progress:{kb_id} {status:"running", total:N, done:0}
    KBAPI2-->>KBView2: {accepted: true}

    loop 轮询进度 (每 2s)
        KBView2->>KBAPI2: GET /{kb_id}/reindex/status
        KBAPI2->>Redis2: GET reindex:progress:{kb_id}
        KBAPI2-->>KBView2: {status, done, total, progress_pct}
    end

    Note over DocSvc2: 后台异步执行
    DocSvc2->>MySQL2: SELECT KBDocument WHERE kb_id={kb_id}
    loop 遍历每个文档
        DocSvc2->>Redis2: GET reindex:cancel:{kb_id}
        alt 已取消
            DocSvc2->>Redis2: SET progress {status:"cancelled"}
            Note over DocSvc2: 退出循环
        end
        DocSvc2->>MySQL2: SELECT KBChunk WHERE document_id={doc_id}
        DocSvc2->>EmbedSvc2: embed_texts(chunk_texts) ← 使用新模型
        EmbedSvc2-->>DocSvc2: new_embeddings[][]
        DocSvc2->>Chroma2: update_chunk_embedding(kb_id, chroma_ids, new_embeddings)
        DocSvc2->>Redis2: HINCRBY progress done 1
    end
    DocSvc2->>MySQL2: UPDATE KnowledgeBase embedding_model={new_model}
    DocSvc2->>Redis2: SET progress {status:"completed"}
    KBView2->>KBView2: 刷新知识库信息

---
    title RAG 对话持久化流程 (P1-1)
    actor User3 as User
    participant RAGView as RAGChatView
    participant KBAPI3 as knowledge_base API
    participant Redis3 as Redis

    User3->>RAGView: 进入 RAG 问答页面
    RAGView->>KBAPI3: GET /chat/sessions
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: SMEMBERS rag:chat:sessions:{user_id}
    Redis3-->>KBAPI3: [session_ids]
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: HGETALL rag:chat:session:meta:{user_id}:{sid} × N
    Redis3-->>KBAPI3: [{title, created_at}]
    KBAPI3-->>RAGView: sessions list

    User3->>RAGView: 选择/新建会话
    RAGView->>KBAPI3: GET /chat/history?session_id={sid}
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: LRANGE rag:chat:history:{user_id}:{sid} 0 -1
    Redis3-->>KBAPI3: [JSON messages]
    KBAPI3-->>RAGView: {messages: [...]}
    RAGView->>RAGView: 渲染历史消息

    User3->>RAGView: 发送新问题
    RAGView->>RAGView: SSE 流式接收回答
    RAGView->>KBAPI3: POST /chat/history {session_id, messages: [...]}
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: DEL + RPUSH rag:chat:history:{user_id}:{sid}
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: EXPIRE 86400
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: SADD rag:chat:sessions:{user_id} {sid}
    KBAPI3->>Redis3: HSET rag:chat:session:meta:{user_id}:{sid}
    KBAPI3-->>RAGView: ok
